          /* Default input styles */
.m-input-field__input {
    cursor: inherit;
    flex: 1 1;
    letter-spacing: .09375rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: color .4s, border-color .4s;
}

/* Input field when it has success */
.m-input-field.has-success .m-input-field__info {
    color: #1db51d;
}

/* Success state border color */
.m-input-field.has-success .m-input-field__input {
    border-color: #1db51d;
}

/* Disabled button */
.is-disabled.a-btn {
    background-color: #fff;
    border-color: #c9d3db;
    box-shadow: none;
    color: #193052;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    opacity: .7;
}

/* Active button when fields have data */
.a-btn {
    align-items: center;
    background-color: #e20000;
    background-image: linear-gradient(180deg, #e51a1a, #cb0000);
    border-radius: .375rem;
    box-shadow: 0 .125rem .3125rem rgba(105, 123, 140, .2);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.9375rem 1.875rem;
}

/* Loading state for button */
.is-loading.a-btn {
    background-color: #0ca6ff;
    background-image: linear-gradient(180deg, #24afff, #0b95e6);
    cursor: progress;
    box-shadow: none;
    text-shadow: 0 .0625rem .375rem rgba(27, 27, 27, .24);
    transition: background-position .4s, box-shadow .4s;
}
